    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Originally a collective term for all the articles of linen, lace, etc. in a woman's wardrobe or trousseau. Now used for women's underwear and nightclothes, particularly high-end women's underwear.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
